cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with generating visual explanations, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also proposes a model to improve the quality of textual explanations, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it aims to ground the generated explanations in the image.
